headline: Invitation Homes Announces $200 Million Joint Venture
summary: DALLAS, November 18, 2024--Invitation Homes Inc. (NYSE: INVH) ("Invitation Homes" or the "Company"), the nation’s premier single-family home leasing and management company, announced today that it has entered into an agreement to form a new joint venture partnership (the "JV") with a leading global real estate investment partner.
